# --- PARKED: the safety explorable + artifacts embedding harmful completions ---
# See PARKED.md. Two reasons, both deliberate:
#   1. these render/contain model-generated harmful compliance text (gun assembly,
#      identity theft, poisoning) — not for a public repo, even weak 360M output;
#   2. the page's copy contradicts its own measured nulls (it says "safety appears"
#      beside a 0/24 badge).
# The series moved to projects/{simulator,sft,preferences} instead. Do not `git add -f`.
